{"tid":1095174,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"蒸魚用腩汁代表豉油 一撚流。","createTime":"2019-04-06T21:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T20:48:45.000Z","uid":171273,"like":6,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"72e562dca35c5e34fb283c7451a1b6d0e7bd1b58","tid":1095174,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T21:53:15.000Z","msg":"睇過杜汶澤喱騷都知<br />\n<br />\n其中一集杜生話佢覺得蒸魚用豉油好浪費條魚<br />\n<br />\n豉油得鹹味<br />\n<br />\n食慣左可能會覺得唔同意<br />\n<br />\n但係理性一諗 又好似係<br />\n<br />\n但係腩汁就唔係得個鹹字 有肉類既天然香味<br />\n<br />\n有油脂既香味 有落香料熬製<br />\n<br />\n尋晚我煮飯諗唔到食乜 下午茶果時買餸靈機一觸食牛腩麵果時叫佢腩汁另上 留左少少夜晚蒸魚 <br />\n<br />\n真係如標題所講 一撚流 絕無誇大<br />\n<br />\n魚既味道帶有隱隱約約牛既肉香<br />\n<br />\n用文字係難以表達呢種從未體驗過既美味<br />\n<br />\n只有親自用味蕾先可以感受到屬於呢道菜既雋永<br />\n<br />\n如果要我一句總結 ：「一半魚，一半牛，就係個鮮字」"},{"pid":"1f1e2c63d5945c1eb4557d792616cac9b7fc35c9","tid":1095174,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T21:53:30.000Z","msg":"代替 標題打錯左"},{"pid":"84fd2ca3291b6c3779ef3a652c457fa3f0685bc2","tid":1095174,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T21:55:39.000Z","msg":"好 ching整來睇下"},{"pid":"7727018644ea33396807c068638d6b2d3d4f2491","tid":1095174,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"84fd2ca3291b6c3779ef3a652c457fa3f0685bc2","tid":1095174,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T21:55:39.000Z","msg":"好 ching整來睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T21:56:14.000Z","msg":"食埋落肚啦"},{"pid":"11080fe3635cc2f5d9746c646a41fdd27c6eca43","tid":1095174,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T21:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cf67e68d1b4ea32204daba4d497d30586b9dea","tid":1095174,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T22:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3d32